column5: FANG FANG buy while you can get it under 100 Permian takeover tgt FANG is a best in breed independent oil gas

Simple idea for those that buy directional callsoptions which is most US retail traders today If you analyze NQF and ESF and figure out where price levels are there and what the sentiment is then generally the FANG stocks that you trade will follow suit Cannot get long AAPL calls if QQQ is bearish etc No indicator tells you that simple concept of understanding market fundamentals
